Term-Screen-Win32 version 0.03
============================

Simple Term::Screen style interface to the Win32::Console::ANSI capabilities


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Win32::Console::ANSI (version 1.00)
  Win32::Console (version 0.191)
  Carp


